_json.gridTitle: Slow Cooker French Onion Chicken Freezer Meal Recipe
_json.description: This scrumptious Slow Cooker French Onion Chicken Freezer Meal Recipe is so good! If you love french onion soup, then you need to try this recipe. It may not be eye appealing once cooked, but it does taste so yummy! I have always loved french onion soup and this combo with chicken is so good! I prepared this freezer meal in an afternoon when doing 15 crockpot freezer meals for my family's dinners.  With back to school activities in full swing, I wanted to make a bunch of prep ahead meals ...
